    &lt;style&gt;
      .mystyle {
        font-size: 25px;
      }
    &lt;/style&gt;
    &lt;div onClick=&#39;this.classList.toggle(&quot;mystyle&quot;);&#39;&gt;
      example1
    &lt;/div&gt;

or maybe add a class to an object you clicked.

    &lt;style&gt;
      .mystyle {
        font-size: 25px;
      }
    &lt;/style&gt;
    &lt;div onClick=&#39;this.classList.add(&quot;mystyle&quot;);&#39;&gt;
